@{b}Known Bugs@{ub}

There is a known bug affecting unnamed codes; Intuition tries to render
those into the listview gadget and runs into zeroed pointers, causing an
Enforcer hit on each. This is a harmless bug, but it is $C0DEDBAD... ;-)

All other bugs are removed with this release. So, if you experience a bug,
please report it to us, if possible with debug tools' output information.
@ENDNODE
@NODE todo "InfraRexx Things to do"
